        "text": "=You are a professional HR assistant composing an interview invitation email.\n\nCANDIDATE:\n- Name: {{ $json.output.name }}\n- Email: {{ $json.output.email }}\n\nPROPOSED INTERVIEW:\n- Date: {{ $json.proposed_interview_day }}\n- Time: {{ $json.proposed_interview_time }}\n\nWRITE a professional, warm HTML email with:\n1. A clear subject line like \"Interview Invitation\"\n2. Congratulate them on being shortlisted\n3. Propose the interview date and time\n4. Ask them to confirm or suggest an alternative date\n5. Sign off as the Recruitment Team\n\nRETURN ONLY valid JSON with these fields:\n{\"subject\": \"...\", \"body\": \"<html>...</html>\"}\n\nNo markdown fences. No extra text. ONLY the JSON object.",
        "options": {}
      },
